  "stem": "<p style=\"text-align: left;\">What is the slope of the graph of <math alttext=\"y equals one fourth left parenthesis 27 x plus 15 right parenthesis plus 7 x\"><mi>y</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mrow><mn>4</mn></mrow></mfrac><mfenced><mrow><mrow><mn>27</mn></mrow><mi>x</mi><mo>+</mo><mrow><mn>15</mn></mrow></mrow></mfenced><mo>+</mo><mrow><mn>7</mn></mrow><mi>x</mi></math>&nbsp;in the&nbsp;<em>xy</em>-plane?</p>",
